OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fthis evening. Otherwise a cloudy night
OL,7,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,8,Fnortheast. Rain turning more
OL,9,Fpersistent across Galloway later.
OL,10,FFreshening southerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,13,Ftime in the morning. Then turning
OL,14,Fbrighter with a few showers. Brisk
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,18,Fcloudy with showers on Saturday.
OL,19,FMainly dry with sunny spells on
OL,20,FSunday. Chance of showery rain on
OL,21,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
